import React, { useEffect } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { Input } from "../component/ui/input"; import { Button } from "../component/ui/button"; import { useNavigate, useParams } from "react-router-dom"; const URI = "http://localhost:8000/usuarios/" const DelectUser = () => { const [Name, setName] = useState(' ') const [last_name, setLastName] = useState(' ') const [user, setUser] = useState(' ') const [email, setEmail] = useState(' ') const [tel, setTel] = useState(' ') const [andress, setAndress] = useState(' ') const navigate = useNavigate() const {id} = useParams() const delectUser = async () => { await axios.delete(URI+id) navigate('/') console.log('Prueba') } useEffect( () => { getUserId() },[]) const getUserId = async () => { const res = await axios.get(URI+id) setName(res.data.Name) setLastName(res.data.lastName) setEmail(res.data.email) setUser(res.data.user) setAndress(res.data.andress) setTel(res.data.tel) } return(<>
) } export default DelectUser
